## recent.base

Cross-type view showing all notes derived from sessions, grouped by their parent session. Excludes session notes themselves (they are the group key) and the dashboard note.

```yaml
filters:
  and:
    - file.hasTag("{{ plugin.common_tag }}")
    - 'file.ext == "md"'
    - 'type != "session-note"'
    - 'type != "dashboard"'

formulas:
  type_icon: 'if(type == "learning", "💡", if(type == "task", "☑️", if(type == "idea", "💭", "📄")))'

properties:
  file.name:
    displayName: "Note"
  formula.type_icon:
    displayName: "Type"
  project:
    displayName: "Project"
  date:
    displayName: "Date"
  session:
    displayName: "Session"

views:
  - type: table
    name: "By Session"
    limit: 6
    order:
      - formula.type_icon
      - file.name
      - project
      - date
    groupBy:
      property: session
      direction: DESC
    summaries:
      file.name: Filled

  - type: table
    name: "Last 30 Days"
    filters:
      and:
        - 'if(date, (today() - date(date)).days <= 30, false)'
    limit: 100
    order:
      - formula.type_icon
      - file.name
      - project
      - date
      - session
    groupBy:
      property: session
      direction: DESC
    summaries:
      file.name: Filled
```

## Dashboard.md

The hub markdown file that embeds Base views. Wikilinks resolve by filename — no placeholder substitution needed regardless of where `.base` files are stored.

```markdown
---
tags:
  - {{ plugin.common_tag }}
  - dashboard
type: dashboard
cssclasses:
  - wide-page
---

